abstract: >-
  Operational and access-related metadata model that governs how DPP and DMP records are stored,
  exposed, shared, and maintained across systems. Defines access levels, security settings,
  data carrier characteristics, longevity policies, interoperability configurations, and
  system integration parameters for the CE-RISE digital product passport and digital material
  passport architecture.
